{"number":17,"verseCount":26,"verses":[[1,["These words spake Jesus, and lifted up his eyes to heaven, and said, Father, the hour is come; glorify thy ",["Son",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship","tg/jesus-christ-divine-sonship"],"."]]],", that thy Son also may ",["glorify",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Mission of","tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"],"."]]]," thee:"]],[2,["As thou hast given him ",["power",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Authority of","tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Power of","tg/jesus-christ-power-of"],"."]]]," over all flesh, that he should give ",["eternal life",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 6:37","nt/john/6.37"],"."]]]," to as many as thou hast ",["given",["study-note-ref","c",[["John 10:29 (27–29)","nt/john/10.29"],"; ",["D&C 50:41","dc-testament/dc/50.41"],"."]]]," him."]],[3,["And this is ",["life",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Eternal Life","tg/eternal-life"],"."]]]," ",["eternal",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Jn. 1:2","nt/1-jn/1.2"],"; ",["2:25","nt/1-jn/2.25"],"; ",["D&C 132:24","dc-testament/dc/132.24"],"."]]],", that they might ",["know",["study-note-ref","c",[["Jer. 9:3","ot/jer/9.3"],"; ",["Hosea 2:20","ot/hosea/2.20"],"; ",["1 Jn. 4:8 (7–8)","nt/1-jn/4.8"],"; ",["D&C 101:16","dc-testament/dc/101.16"],". ",["TG God, Knowledge about","tg/god-knowledge-about"],"; ",["Objectives","tg/objectives"],"; ",["Testimony","tg/testimony"],"."]]]," thee the only true ",["God",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Godhead","tg/godhead"],"."]]],", and Jesus Christ, whom thou hast ",["sent",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Jesus Christ, Messenger of the Covenant","tg/jesus-christ-messenger-of-the-covenant"],"."]]],"."]],[4,["I have ",["glorified",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 65:6","dc-testament/dc/65.6"],"; ",["76:43 (40–43)","dc-testament/dc/76.43"],"."]]]," thee on the earth: I have ",["finished",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 19:2","dc-testament/dc/19.2"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"."]]]," the work which thou gavest me to do."]],[5,["And now, O Father, glorify thou me with thine own self with the ",["glory",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Celestial Glory","tg/celestial-glory"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Glory of","tg/jesus-christ-glory-of"],"."]]]," which I had with thee ",["before",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Foreordained","tg/jesus-christ-foreordained"],"; ",["Man, Antemortal Existence of","tg/man-antemortal-existence-of"],"."]]]," the world was."]],[6,["I have manifested thy name unto the men which thou gavest me ",["out",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Kgs. 8:53","ot/1-kgs/8.53"],"; ",["3 Ne. 15:19 (19–20)","bofm/3-ne/15.19"],"."]]]," of the world: thine they were, and thou gavest them me; and they have kept thy word."]],[7,["Now they have known that all things whatsoever thou hast ",["given",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Relationships with the Father","tg/jesus-christ-relationships-with-the-father"],"."]]]," me are of thee."]],[8,["For I have given unto them the ",["words",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 18:18","ot/deut/18.18"],"; ",["John 6:68","nt/john/6.68"],". ",["TG Revelation","tg/revelation"],"."]]]," which thou gavest me; and they have received ",["them,",["clarity-word"]]," and have known surely that I ",["came",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 8:42","nt/john/8.42"],"; ",["16:28 (27–28, 30)","nt/john/16.28"],"; ",["Gal. 4:4","nt/gal/4.4"],"."]]]," out from thee, and they have ",["believed",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]]," that thou didst send me."]],[9,["I ",["pray",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," for them: I pray not for the world, but for them which ",["thou",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 27:14","dc-testament/dc/27.14"],"; ",["84:63","dc-testament/dc/84.63"],"."]]]," hast given me; for they are thine."]],[10,["And all mine are thine, and thine are mine; and I am glorified in them."]],[11,["And now I am no more in the world, but these are in the ",["world",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Earth, Purpose of","tg/earth-purpose-of"],"."]]],", and I come to thee. Holy Father, keep through thine own name those whom thou hast given me, that they may be ",["one",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Unity","tg/unity"],"."]]],", as we ",["are.",["clarity-word"]]]],[12,["While I was with them in the world, I kept them in thy name: those that thou gavest me I have kept, and ",["none",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 6:39","nt/john/6.39"],"; ",["18:9","nt/john/18.9"],"."]]]," of them is ",["lost",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 50:42","dc-testament/dc/50.42"],"."]]],", but the son of ",["perdition",["study-note-ref","c",[["3 Ne. 27:32","bofm/3-ne/27.32"],". ",["TG Damnation","tg/damnation"],"; ",["Death, Spiritual, Second","tg/death-spiritual-second"],"; ",["Hell","tg/hell"],"."]]],"; that the scripture might be fulfilled."]],[13,["And now come I to thee; and ",["",1358],"these things I speak in the world, that they might have my ",["joy",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]]," fulfilled in themselves."]],[14,["I have given them thy word; and the world hath hated them, because they are not of the world, even as I am not of the world."]],[15,["I pray not that thou shouldest take them out of the ",["world",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG World","tg/world"],"."]]],", but that thou shouldest ",["keep",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Refuge","tg/refuge"],"."]]]," them from the ",["evil",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Evil","tg/evil"],"."]]],"."]],[16,["They are not of the ",["world",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Worldliness","tg/worldliness"],"."]]],", even as I am not of the world."]],[17,[["Sanctify",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Sanctification","tg/sanctification"],"."]]]," them through thy ",["truth",["study-note-ref","b",[["Jacob 4:13","bofm/jacob/4.13"],"."]]],": thy word is ",["truth",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Sam. 7:28","ot/2-sam/7.28"],"; ",["Ps. 119:142","ot/ps/119.142"],". ",["TG Truth","tg/truth"],"."]]],"."]],[18,["As thou hast ",["sent",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Authority of","tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"],"."]]]," me into the world, even so have I also sent them into the world."]],[19,["And for their sakes I ",["sanctify",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"."]]]," myself, that they also might be sanctified through the truth."]],[20,["Neither ",["pray",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," I for these alone, but for them also which shall ",["believe",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 45:5","dc-testament/dc/45.5"],"."]]]," on me through their word;"]],[21,["That they all may be ",["one",["study-note-ref","a",[["4 Ne. 1:17 (15–17)","bofm/4-ne/1.17"],"; ",["D&C 38:27","dc-testament/dc/38.27"],"."]]],"; as thou, ",["Father",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Godhead","tg/godhead"],"; ",["God the Father, Elohim","tg/god-the-father-elohim"],"."]]],", ",["art",["clarity-word"]]," in me, and I in thee, that they also may be ",["one",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 35:2","dc-testament/dc/35.2"],"; ",["Moses 6:68","pgp/moses/6.68"],"."]]]," in us: that the world may believe that thou hast sent me."]],[22,["And the glory which thou gavest me I have given them; that they may be ",["one",["study-note-ref","a",[["Gal. 2:20","nt/gal/2.20"],"."]]],", even as we are ",["one",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 93:3","dc-testament/dc/93.3"],"."]]],":"]],[23,["I in them, and thou in me, that they may be made ",["perfect",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Perfection","tg/perfection"],"."]]]," in one; and that the world may know that thou hast sent me, and hast ",["loved",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Love of","tg/god-love-of"],"."]]]," them, as thou hast loved me."]],[24,["Father, I will that they also, whom thou hast given me, be with me where I am; that they may behold my glory, which thou hast given me: for thou lovedst me before the foundation of the world."]],[25,["O righteous Father, the world hath not ",["known",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Knowledge about","tg/god-knowledge-about"],"."]]]," thee: but I have known thee, and these have known that thou hast sent me."]],[26,["And I have ",["declared",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Preaching","tg/preaching"],"."]]]," unto them thy ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Name","tg/name"],"."]]],", and will declare ",["it:",["clarity-word"]]," that the ",["love",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG God, Love of","tg/god-love-of"],"."]]]," wherewith thou hast ",["loved",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Jesus Christ, Relationships with the Father","tg/jesus-christ-relationships-with-the-father"],"."]]]," me may be in them, and I in them."]]],"volume":"nt"}